<i>adjective</i>: 허풍스럽다 [허풍스럽따] <i>noun</i>: 흰소리 [힌소리] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>허풍스럽다 [허풍스럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>boastful; bragging; braggart</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동이 실제보다 지나치게 부풀려져 믿기 어려운 데가 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Words or actions that are excessively exaggerated and hard to believe.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>흰소리 [힌소리]</dt><br>
<dd>bluffing; bragging; big talk; hot air</dd><br>
<dd>전혀 근거가 없이 자랑으로 떠벌리거나 잘난 체하며 버릇없이 굴며 허풍을 떠는 말.</dd><br>
<dd>A completely baseless, boastful remark, or bragging while showing off and acting rudely.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>